title: Can I Solve this Minecraft Puzzle in 24 Hours?
author: Parrot
description:
A few days ago, I got a message from a mysterious Twitter user telling me to go visit a location on the LifeSteal SMP, a Minecraft Server where you can steal other players' hearts... Can I solve this Minecraft Puzzle in 24 Hours?

Like ParrotX2 and his LifeSteal SMP Series where he broke bedrock or blew up 2000 TNT. Not Technoblade / TommyInnit / or any other Dream SMP member. This is a new and original Minecraft idea like HermitCraft or LastLife with Grian and MumboJumbo. Survival is harder than Hardcore Minecraft because PVP is on. 

LifeSteal Members in this Video: @Vort3xDragon @rekrap2 @PrinceZam @Sponker @Pangi @roshambogames @Spoke @Vitalasy
